text: I want an easy strategy that doesn't take that long to manage and makes me better than market returns with lower risk. Whenever I hear stuff like that, I always say, same, dog, same, on the same exact thing. But it doesn't exist if you approach trading with this kind of really skewed expectation, it's literally going to fail. There is no way to success with that kind of expectation. So if you develop healthy expectations of markets, then your ability to actually hit them will go up. You know how I sell it.
